reviews.text:
Absolutely awful on every single level. Though the service is the most disgusting. Waitress spilled our food and drinks all over us upon serving and blamed it all on us. Refused to let us know who the manager is, when we approached the other waiter he looked at us then just pretended didn’t see us. Assistant manager finally came and did try to apologise, but when the actual manager came he absolutely didn’t even care. 
On top of all these, food was awful we felt sick after.
Nice place, nice food, and with excellent services.
One of my favorite places to eat, a good price, delicious food, English menu and an uplifting atmosphere!!

Need to wait more than 30 mins on Saturday tea time. There has a Japanese chef here, waitress are nice, foods are delivered very quickly although the noodles are small portions and waitress are not very familiar with the menu and they amended our order for third times.

Taste ok and price is fair.
Above average Japanese food special in Okinawa style.
Staff are very polite and helpful.

result.name: Antoshimo Café & Bakery

reviews.text:
吃到了期間限定的一人餐...一個套餐含一個免費的甜品。大概幾個月就會推出一次吧。
本身很喜歡走日式路線的餐廳，因為陪友人已經吃過這家幾次了。說到主菜的話我覺得套餐的選擇算是蠻多的，但調味上不太符合我的口味，比較普通。但喜歡日系料理的人應該來試一下。
我很喜歡他們的甜品，鹹甜的焦糖醬冬甩搭配雲尼拿冰淇淋很好，用冰淇淋中和掉冬甩的鹹味，很剛好。這個一人餐很推，吃完甜品覺得心情很好哈哈XD
而且位置坐得算舒服，整日評分有拉高，價錢也是中等。

Absolutely awful on every single level. Though the service is the most disgusting. Waitress spilled our food and drinks all over us upon serving and blamed it all on us. Refused to let us know who the manager is, when we approached the other waiter he looked at us then just pretended didn’t see us. Assistant manager finally came and did try to apologise, but when the actual manager came he absolutely didn’t even care. 
On top of all these, food was awful we felt sick after.
Nice place, nice food, and with excellent services.
蕃薯條，配黑糖，好味
